      "rationale": "Young's modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus derived from tensile coupon testing of Ti-6Al-4V ELI material lot used in bench specimens. UHMWPE block properties from literature with ±10% sensitivity sweep. Screw geometry from CMM measurements (±0.01 mm). Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (n=500). Required level 3 achieved."
