      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single compressive-bending load profile per ASTM F1717; multiple load levels not explored. PBS immersion at 37 °C applied. Inter-laboratory reproducibility confirmed (CV <5% between labs). Single test condition limits achieved level to 2, below required level of 3. This shortfall is acknowledged and accepted given the standardized nature of F1717 protocol.",
