      "rationale": "Measured specimen dimensions, material lot properties, and fixture geometry used directly as model inputs. Crosshead displacement rate mapped to quasi-static loading assumption (inertial effects <0.1%). PBS immersion temperature modeled via temperature-dependent UHMWPE properties. Full input-to-experiment mapping table documented. Required level 3 achieved."
