      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in ASTM F1717 and directly relevant to clinical performance (subsidence, screw fracture, loss of fixation). Regulatory relevance confirmed by FDA guidance on spinal implant mechanical testing. Required level 3 achieved."
